<!DOCTYPE>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
        <title>Actionable emails e.g. reset password</title>
    </head>

    <body itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/EmailMessage">
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <div style="font-size:15px; color: black;">
                        <p style="margin: 0;">
                            Hello <b>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</b>,
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;">
                            In order to change your password for EGT's Control System Website, please click <a href="{{resetPasswordUrl}}"><b>here</b></a> or paste the following link into your browser:
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 0;">
                            <div style="overflow-wrap: break-word; word-wrap: break-word; -ms-word-break: break-all; word-break: break-all; word-break: break-word; -ms-hyphens: auto; -moz-hyphens: auto; -webkit-hyphens: auto; hyphens: auto;">
                                <a href="{{resetPasswordUrl}}">{{resetPasswordUrl}}</a>
                            </div>
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
                            This link will expire in 24 hours, so be sure to use it right away.<br>
                            The currently supported browsers are Google Chrome and Mozilla Firefox.
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;">
                            If you haven't requested a password reset, please <a href="{{openMailClientUrl}}">contact</a> us and we will investigate the matter further.
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;">
                            The Control System's Team
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </body>
</html>